N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 400.15 - Referee tests of pressure compensated counters

State Regulations

Pressure compensated counters shall not be removed from

Shuntflo meters undergoing referee tests and shall be tested in the presence
and under the direction of a representative of the
commission. Notes
